00:40:12.500 --> 00:40:15.580
for-- I mean dense,
high-density cities are not

00:40:15.580 --> 00:40:21.140
a prerequisite and probably not
the best place to really move

00:40:21.140 --> 00:40:23.010
the need with innovation.

00:40:23.010 --> 00:40:26.330
And San Francisco has
certainly some startups,

00:40:26.330 --> 00:40:27.840
and I think the
scene has shifted

00:40:27.840 --> 00:40:30.050
