00:40:30.050 --> 00:40:32.780
but I'm not sure of the
cause and effect there.

00:40:32.780 --> 00:40:35.050
So maybe you can talk
about this a bit.

00:40:35.050 --> 00:40:37.258
GREGORY FERENSTEIN: No,
