The idea is that especially
Silicon Valley, when

00:40:39.520 --> 00:40:44.410
it started in the '60s and then
kind of grow, '70s and '80s,

00:40:44.410 --> 00:40:46.990
tended to be a little
bit more suburban.

00:40:46.990 --> 00:40:50.280
So why are cities necessary?

