One is, relatively
speaking, the Bay Area

00:40:56.740 --> 00:40:58.667
is still extremely
dense, compared

00:40:58.667 --> 00:40:59.875
to the middle of the country.

00:40:59.875 --> 00:41:03.510
Where I'm from, Omaha,
Nebraska and the rest of these,

00:41:03.510 --> 00:41:05.490
even though it
doesn't look as dense

00:41:05.490 --> 00:41:08.310
because there's kind of
single family home houses,

00:41:08.310 --> 00:41:10.490
there's a lot of them.

00:41:10.490 --> 00:41:14.770
And no one really has
big yards here, right?

00:41:14.770 --> 00:41:17.220
So compared to the rest of
the country and in New York

00:41:17.220 --> 00:41:19.450
as well, still relatively dense.

00:41:22.050 --> 00:41:26.820
